Sentencas: In this study, a typical three-dimensional model of single channel mono-block-layer build solid oxide fuel cell (MOLB-type SOFC) was developed.
Titulo: Effect of Rib Width and Cathode Thickness on the Performance of MOLB-Type SOFC

Sentencas: The effects of rib width and cathode thickness on the species concentration distribution, electrochemical performance, and temperature distribution of MOLB-type SOFC were investigated.
Titulo: Effect of Rib Width and Cathode Thickness on the Performance of MOLB-Type SOFC

Sentencas: The results show that adapting a smaller rib width can improve the uniformity of gas distribution, decrease the concentration polarization, and improve the output performance of SOFC.
Titulo: Effect of Rib Width and Cathode Thickness on the Performance of MOLB-Type SOFC

Sentencas: The performance of the cell can be significantly improved by thickening the cathode electrode.
Titulo: Effect of Rib Width and Cathode Thickness on the Performance of MOLB-Type SOFC

Sentencas: When the cathode thickness is 0.45 mm, the maximum output power density is improved by 53.69% compared with that at 0.15 mm.
Titulo: Effect of Rib Width and Cathode Thickness on the Performance of MOLB-Type SOFC

Sentencas: With the increase of the cathode thickness, the enhancement of the cell performance by increasing the cathode thickness gradually decreases.
Titulo: Effect of Rib Width and Cathode Thickness on the Performance of MOLB-Type SOFC

Sentencas: In addition, as the cathode thickness increases, the concentration polarization and temperature gradient of the cell gradually rise, while the activation polarization gradually decreases.
Titulo: Effect of Rib Width and Cathode Thickness on the Performance of MOLB-Type SOFC
